<TEXT>
<P>
 Comedy writer Tony Peyser, on the juror who brought a dictionary into the 
deliberation room at Rodney King's civil trial to look up the word 
reprehensible . When the trial judge lectured the juror and announced that the 
dictionary would be confiscated, the juror was overheard saying, "Whew! I 
thought he was going to take it away from me." 
