<HEADLINE>
<P>
STEFFE GROUNDS HIMSELF, MOVES ON TO QUINCY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Matt Steffe, a former Hart High forward and member of the 1992 Times' 
All-Valley basketball team, has transferred from the Air Force Academy prep 
school to Quincy University in Illinois. 
</P>
<P>
 Steffe (6-feet-7, 202 pounds) averaged 15.9 points and 6.5 rebounds per game 
last season.  
</P>
<P>
 He joins a team that was 19-9 last season and earned a bid to the NCAA 
Division II tournament. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA052094-0114 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 043496 </DOCID>
