<P>
 Princess Diana is being hailed as a hero for aiding a drowning man. 
</P>
<P>
 The princess was on her way home from a jog in London's Regents Park on Sunday 
when tourists flagged her car and said someone had fallen into a nearby lake. 
Diana reportedly told her chauffeur to call police, then dashed to the bank of 
